Package: PingMeUp
Title: Tools for Exploring AFTT Table Tennis Data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-23
Authors@R: 
    person("Geoffrey", "Caruso", 
           email = "geoffrey.caruso@uni.lu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to scrape, clean, analyse and map table 
    tennis data from the AFTT website. The package is developed for 
    methodological exploration, teaching reproducible workflows to 
    geography students, and supporting club- or federation-level 
    analysis of points, rankings, performance and geographic patterns. 
    This is an independent, non-official project; for official data 
    and rankings, refer to the AFTT Data Portal.
License: MIT + file LICENSE 
